## 🟡 MEDIUM — Missing Scenarios

No tests exist for these behaviors at all:

| Gap | Production Risk |
|---|---|
| `UpdatePrice` with non-existent SKU | Should throw `KeyNotFoundException` — never tested |
| `GetProduct` with non-existent SKU | Should return `null` — never tested |
| `Search` with no matches | Empty list behavior untested |
| `ImportFromCsv` with multi-line input | Only single-line tested |
| `ImportFromCsv` with malformed data | No error-path coverage |
| `ApplyBulkDiscount` with 0% or 100% | Boundary values untested |

